    <item>
      <title>Interview for the &#34;Impressa e Auditável&#34; newsletter</title>
      <link>/en/blog/impressa_auditavel/</link>
      <pubDate>Thu, 11 Dec 2025 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>/en/blog/impressa_auditavel/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;Interview for the edition &lt;a href=&#34;https://impressa.news/22-pesquisas-fascismos-e-brasil/&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;#22 | Pesquisas, Fascismos e Brasil&lt;/a&gt; of the newsletter &lt;a href=&#34;https://impressa.news/&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;&lt;em&gt;Impressa e Auditável&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/a&gt;, produced by &lt;a href=&#34;https://bsky.app/profile/lucaslago.projeto7c0.com.br&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;Lucas Lago&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The interview focused on a &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.labourtogether.uk/all-reports/measuring-what-matters?ref=impressa.news&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;report&lt;/a&gt; by the think tank &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.labourtogether.uk/&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;&lt;em&gt;Labour Together&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/a&gt; on how to measure a country&amp;rsquo;s main problem or concern.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We also briefly discussed the article &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.cambridge.org/core/journals/political-science-research-and-methods/article/does-accommodation-work-mainstream-party-strategies-and-the-success-of-radical-right-parties/5C3476FCD26B188C7399ADD920D71770&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;&amp;ldquo;Does accommodation work? Mainstream party strategies and the success of radical right parties&amp;rdquo;&lt;/a&gt;, published in the journal &lt;em&gt;Political Science Research and Methods&lt;/em&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The full interview is &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Ovi3EbV0wdQ&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;available on YouTube&lt;/a&gt; (in Portuguese).&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div style=&#34;position: relative; padding-bottom: 56.25%; height: 0; overflow: hidden;&#34;&gt;
